function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
	if #T_INSIDERADIUS > 0 then
		for i=1, #T_INSIDERADIUS do
			if	T_INSIDERADIUS[i] == idActor then

			end
		end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	if #T_INSIDERADIUS > 0 then
		for i=1, #T_INSIDERADIUS do
			if	T_INSIDERADIUS[i] == idActorKilled then
				Hydra.EventSendToActor("QST_Scos_Crone_Q3_KilledInside", idSelf, idSelf)
				Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtTarget(idActorKilled, ID_WOODWRAITH, s_POWER_ONDEATH)
				table.remove(T_INSIDERADIUS, i)
			end
		end
	end
end
